{
  "stem": "11272.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And we were dragging it out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And just as we loaded it into one of the-- where a bomb crate was, where a bomb fell, it went off.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "If it would have gone off one second earlier, I wouldn't have been here to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But-- those-- those bombings gave us a little reprieve.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Because we didn't have to work so hard at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We were just able to stand outside, and hopefully it was raining or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Then we could relax a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We worked in packaging and-- and carrying those gauges and storing them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Mostly we did only heavy manual labor, nothing else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- there were a lot of them, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know for a fact that we sabotaged a railroad tracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, one of the gangs that worked with me that was in our barrack, they worked on repairing the railroad tracks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And just as the SS men went to whistle and line up up front, he managed-- he-- he thought he saw them tied down, but instead of that, he managed to push the rail onto the side.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, when the train came, the whole train was derailed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was a lot of punishment-- a lot of punishment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- but we-- we had constant punishment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The punishment, to us, was just a-- a routine thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they-- they had all kinds of excuses to punish us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If the weather was no good, they punished us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If the weather was too warm, they punished us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If the weather was too cold, they punished us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took their frustrations out on us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
